                <h2>A webinar on high availability and data safety in messaging</h2>
                <h2><a href="https://tanzu.vmware.com/content/webinars/jun-11-ha-and-data-safety-in-messaging-quorum-queues-in-rabbitmq?utm_campaign=Global_BT_Q221_RabbitMQ-Data-Safety-in-Messaging&amp;utm_source=rabbitmq&amp;utm_medium=website" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Learn more</a></h2>
